        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p> <b>Korean War</b> <b>Divided Families Reunification Act</b> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to periodically report to Congress on its consultations with South Korea&nbsp;on potential opportunities to reunite Korean Americans with family in North Korea. The State Department's Special Envoy on North Korean Human Rights Issues shall periodically report to Congress on its&nbsp;consultations with representatives of Korean Americans with family in North Korea on reunification efforts. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
